      <body>
         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">Melbourne ¶ 7/6/88 ¶ T.R. Wilson Esqr ¶ Undersecretary. ¶ Sir...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">88.06.07</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">To Thomas Wilson<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
            </p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">L88/5602, unit 346, VPRS 3992/P inward registered correspondence, VA 475 Chief Secretary's Department, Public Record Office, Victoria.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">Melbourne</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">7/6/88</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">T.R. Wilson Esqr</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Undersecretary.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Sir</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>As the service-year under the Government is again drawing to a close, I have the honor to report, that I feel myself quite capable to continue the performance of the duties of Governments<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Botanist in all its branches, and would therefore solicit the hon. the Chief Secretary and through him the Government, to allow me to continue my position, giving myself the assurance of my utmost desire, to carry out the various obligations in this branch of the service with zeal and close application.<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn0" n="1">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>On 13 June 1888,<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>H. Moors, for the Under Secretary, sent to M the minute: 'The Government Botanist's name is included in the list of officers who have attained the age of sixty years and whose services it is recommended should be further retained'.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>M replied the next day 'with best thanks'.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">I have the honor to be,</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Sir, your <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>obedient servant</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. von Mueller,</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Gov. Botanist.</p>
         </div>
      </body>
